  "texts": [
    "At the end of the 10-day period, each response was compared against the correct answers outlined in the guideline.",
    "Pearson Chi-Square tests were applied to analyze the distribution of the answers and to assess the relationships between the platforms.",
    "ResultsA total of 1,380 responses were obtained, with 60 responses provided for each question.",
    "Statistical analyses for responses collected at different times of the day and overall revealed significant relationships between the platforms and the accuracy of the answers (Table 2) (p < 0.05).",
    "Among the platforms, ChatGPT-4 with the PDF plugin had the highest correct response rate (98.1%), while Gemini had the lowest (48%)."
